dct_title_s: Præfecturæ Leucopetranæ delineatio geographica, urbes, oppida, vicos, pagos, limitesque nova ratione complectens
dct_description_sm: Map of the Saxony-Anhalt region of Germany centering on Weissenfels. Relief shown pictorially. In margins: Register derer auff dieser Charte befindlichen Orte im Amte Weissenfels.
